                        <interp inst="t18460921-name-832" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS JOHNSON</persName>
                  </hi>. Whatman brought me these parts of a bedstead on the morning of the 14th and sold them to me—he was alone—it was not found at my premises—I have never bought anything of Rickards.</p>
